    <description descriptionType="Abstract">Tabular dataset (6,607 records; 20 variables) for student performance analytics. Includes demographics and learning-context factors and the outcome Exam_Score. Intended for regression, uncertainty estimation, and budgeted Top-K screening / governance routing experiments. Missing values occur only in three categorical fields (Teacher_Quality, Parental_Education_Level, Distance_from_Home).</description>
